  dialogueHidesSubmit: 0
  lines:
  - Y-yes my documents, here.
  - "I\u2019m sorry, I\u2019ve just come down from working at the orphanage, and
    the stress there among the children is kinda getting to me\u2026."
  - "But, there\u2019s this lovely girl we\u2019ve had in for university placements,
    and she\u2019s just been amazing with calming their nerves, helping them out,
    making them feel safe."
  - 'Just seeing it has helped me aswell, that and how smooth and easy this whole
    evacuation process has been. '
  - "So\u2026 yeah, thanks for your efforts, aswell."
  - 'You: No problem, glad to hear your doing better.'
